		 <p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、问：什么是海伦凯勒积分商城？<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">答：海伦凯勒积分商城是海伦凯勒会员专享的积分兑换平台。会员累积积分达到某一商品兑换标准时，即可依照海伦凯勒积分商城相应的兑换规则申请兑换商品。网站将即时从会员账户内扣减相应的积分和话费。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、问：参加积分兑换有什么要求？<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
<p><span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">
<p class="p0" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">答：需要满足以下几点</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">a、&nbsp;只有参与</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">短信积分</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">活动（即K计划）的用户才可累积积分。</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p0" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; background: rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">b、&nbsp;话费支付仅限指定区域的中国移动用户（黑龙江、吉林、辽宁、河南、陕西、山西、甘肃、湖北、四川、上海、海南、江苏、广西、福建）。其他用户可使用支付宝进行支付。</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">c、&nbsp;一旦</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">支付成功</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，积分即被扣除，即使</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">取消订单</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，积分亦无法返还。</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">d、&nbsp;产品型号和</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">价格</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">会定期调整，请以实际显示产品为准，无法按个人需求订购。</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">e、&nbsp;注册时验证码接收稍慢，请耐心等待。</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">f、&nbsp;活动流程请参看登录后的详细描述页面。</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">g、&nbsp;配送时间为7个工作日内发出，如有特殊情况，公司会单独联系。</span><span style="font-family: '微软雅黑'; color: rgb(144,144,144); font-size: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
