<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、问：什么是中国移动话费支付业务？<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">答：中国移动话费支付业务也称本地通信账户支付业务，具体是：用户使用手机账户内的话费进行小额支付交易（仅从用户预存或支付到该账户的金额中扣除，不包括移动奖励、赠送、返还的费用以及专款等），来兑换商品及服务。用户可通过手机、电脑等操作方式。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、问：中国移动话费支付的业务范围？<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">答：中国移动全球通后付费用户，动感地带及神州行的预付费用户，支持省份及城市详见下表。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、问：通过中国移动话费支付方式兑换商品，是否有限制？<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">答：存在交易限额及其他限制条件，具体如下：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p>
<table class="MsoNormalTable" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="width: 702px; border-collapse: collapse; height: 777px; mso-yfti-tbllook: 1184; mso-padding-alt: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm">
