<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">6</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、问：中国移动话费支付兑换商品具体流程是什么？<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">答：具体流程为：<span lang="EN-US"><br />
</span>步骤<span lang="EN-US">1</span>：注册成为海伦凯勒积分商城会员；<span lang="EN-US"><br />
</span>步骤<span lang="EN-US">2</span>：选择您喜欢的商品，填写您的收货地址，生成订单；；<span lang="EN-US"><br />
</span>步骤<span lang="EN-US">2</span>：付款页面选择支付，并确认支付；<span lang="EN-US"><br />
</span>步骤<span lang="EN-US">3</span>：手机号码收到确认付款短信：请回复数字<span lang="EN-US">***</span>确认支付，您将通过通信账户兑换海伦凯勒积分商城产品，费用<span lang="EN-US">**</span>元。客服<span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">4008950098<br style="mso-special-character: line-break" />
</span></span>步骤<span lang="EN-US">4</span>：按照短信提示回复数字&ldquo;<span lang="EN-US">***</span>&rdquo;确认支付；<span lang="EN-US"><br />
</span>步骤<span lang="EN-US">5</span>：收到成功支付短信，完成支付；<span lang="EN-US"><br />
</span>步骤<span lang="EN-US">6</span>：接下来您需要等待我们为您发货，如果有问题可以拨打客服电话：<span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">4008950098</span></span>。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">7</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、问：在支付的过程中有疑问，如何进行咨询？<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">答：由于话费支付由联动优势公司提供，因此若在海伦凯勒积分商城网上兑换商品的支付过程中有任何问题，可与<span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">海伦凯勒客服<span lang="EN-US">4008950098</span></span>进行联系。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">8</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、问：兑换商品后，何时进行扣费？多久可以查到余额有变化？<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">答：在用户二次确认短信回复成功后，系统将同步完成扣费，用户在兑换商品一个小时后将可以查询到余额变动情况。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">9</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、问：兑换成功后，是否支持退换票？<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">答：很抱歉，由于网站系统和积分系统是直连的，并且话费支付属于特殊支付；因此一旦兑换成功，不支持退换。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">10</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、问：我的话费余额还有<span lang="EN-US">50</span>元，却无法兑换<span lang="EN-US">45</span>元（包含了运费）的商品，返回的信息为&ldquo;您的话费余额不足&rdquo;，这是怎么回事？<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">答：为了保障移动客户使用保持通讯的基本需求，运营商对话费支付业务设置了最低话费保障金额限制，当用户在完成当次支付后存在话费余额最低要求，未达到此标准的号码不能进行交易，详情请见问题<span lang="EN-US">5</span>。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">11</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、问：我手机卡中余额充足，第一次兑换成功后，马上进行了第二次兑换，却没有成功，为什么？<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">答：因为话费支付业务为了保障用户的账户安全，设置了交易时间间隔，即您成功交易一次后要等一定时间后才能进行第二笔交易，详情请见问题<span lang="EN-US">5</span>。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">12</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、问：如果用户迟迟未收到二次确认短信或着商品信息短信，该怎么办？<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">答：这种情况有可能是网络延时，可以建议用户耐心的等待，如果还未收到相关信息，可将相关问题反映给<span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">海伦凯勒客服<span lang="EN-US">4008950098</span></span>，进行配合查询。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">13</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">、问：如何开通&ldquo;本地通信账户支付&rdquo;（即移动话费支付）业务，业务资费是多少？<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background: white; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; color: #909090; font-size: 9pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">答：只要您是中国移动用户，系统将默认自动开通&ldquo;本地通信账户支付业务。<span lang="EN-US"><br />
</span>本地通信账户支付业务资费：<span lang="EN-US"><br />
</span>●无月功能服务费；<span lang="EN-US"><br />
</span>●用户通过短信方式使用业务产生的通信费由中国移动按照现行短信资费标准收取。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
